<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">忘记了密码?</div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <form class="new_user" id="new_user" action="/forgot_password_email" accept-charset="UTF-8" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="post" />
      <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="<%= get_csrf_token() %>" />
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="email" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Email" name="user[email]" id="user_email">
        <p class="form-text text-muted">此功能将会发送一个找回密码的特别链接到你的邮箱，通过改链接可以进入重置密码的页面。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-actions">
        <input type="submit" name="commit" value="找回密码" class="btn btn-primary">
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>